<paragraph pageNumber="792">
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="792">Note:</emphasis>
Turrill (in 
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="792">Izv. Bulg. Bot. Druz.</emphasis>
7: 23-25. 1936) discussed the history of this name and provided detailed descriptions of the material on sheets 520.1 and 520.2 (LINN). He identified Bulgarian material as conspecific with that on 520.1, adding that 
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="792">R. rhapontium</emphasis>
L. is the correct name for this taxon. However, his statement is insufficiently explicit to effect formal typification.
</paragraph>
